{"id":"errors/NG0403","title":"NG0403: 用於引導的 NgModule 未指定應初始化哪個元件。","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng0403-an-ngmodule-that-was-used-for-bootstrapping-does-not-specify-which-component-should-be-initialized\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7kdrz29vfz7hsjj26vdqdckq3\">NG0403: 用於引導的 NgModule 未指定應初始化哪個元件。<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0403#ng0403-an-ngmodule-that-was-used-for-bootstrapping-does-not-specify-which-component-should-be-initialized\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  \n  \n\n  <div class=\"error-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0403#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5n4myj3dledcqnaczaqyubi7v\">這個錯誤意味著用於引導應用程式的 NgModule 中缺少 Angular 繼續引導時所需的關鍵訊息。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6alfe55bnmbsza5lvws0a9hgh\">當 <code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> 註解中的 <code>bootstrap</code> 屬性缺失（或是空陣列）並且該 NgModule 類別上沒有定義 <code>ngDoBootstrap</code> 生命週期鉤子時，就會發生本錯誤。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"67qjetplrn1kw65egp22ffi4c\">可以在<a href=\"guide/bootstrapping\">本指南</a>中找到有關引導過程的更多訊息。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"arzd8spphyexzbiuw3akgoz23\">以下範例將引發錯誤。</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  declarations: [AppComponent],\n  imports: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a>, AppRoutingModule],\n  providers: [],\n})\nexport class AppModule {}\n\n// The `AppModule` is used for bootstrapping, but the `@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule#bootstrap\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule.bootstrap</a>` field is missing.\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowser</a>().bootstrapModule(AppModule);\n</code-example>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a>({\n  declarations: [AppComponent],\n  imports: [<a href=\"api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">BrowserModule</a>, AppRoutingModule],\n  providers: [],\n  bootstrap: [],\n})\nexport class AppModule {}\n\n// The `AppModule` is used for bootstrapping, but the `@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule#bootstrap\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule.bootstrap</a>` field contains an empty array.\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\" class=\"code-anchor\">platformBrowser</a>().bootstrapModule(AppModule);\n</code-example>\n\n  </div>\n\n\n  \n  <br>\n\n  <div class=\"debugging\">\n    <h2 id=\"debugging-the-error\">如何排除本錯誤<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"errors/NG0403#debugging-the-error\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"30p5uso61kodd3s91f041snzn\">請確保用於引導的 NgModule 設定正確：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"crvh37n7r97n6fd6zyh8ckqbi\"><code>@<a href=\"api/core/NgModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModule</a></code> 註解中存在 <code>bootstrap</code> 屬性（且包含非空陣列）</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"9mh178fbda8xr57vlchugajv8\">或者 NgModule 類別中存在 <code>ngDoBootstrap</code> 方法。</li>\n</ul>\n\n  </div>\n  \n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - errors\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/NgModule#bootstrap\n - api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\n - api/platform-browser/platformBrowser\n - errors/NG0403#debugging-the-error\n - errors/NG0403#description\n - errors/NG0403#ng0403-an-ngmodule-that-was-used-for-bootstrapping-does-not-specify-which-component-should-be-initialized\n - guide/bootstrapping\n-->"}